ed", "cluster": "mineral_science", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "360cc497-a9f5-42aa-b2cd-5b27e62988c3", "path": "/science/minerals/volcanic-origin", "title": "Volcanic Origin Minerals – From Magma to Microdose", "status": "published", "cluster": "mineral_science", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "8fe7a09f-375c-4d9c-814b-784601c719b6", "path": "/science/minerals/trace-mineral-showdown", "title": "Trace Mineral Supplement Showdown – Ocean, Seaweed, Fulvic, Salt, Mica", "status": "published", "cluster": "mineral_science", "priority": "P2", "template": "longform_comparison"}, {"id": "40e4aa58-47f7-4a2f-a641-340afb6d55d9", "path": "/science/minerals/missing-minerals-enzymes", "title": "The Missing Minerals in Enzymes – 91% Still Unmapped", "status": "published", "cluster": "mineral_science", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}]}, {"name": "listPages", "result": [{"id": "4a5981e6-7fd8-4a1f-949a-42534bd2d1c1", "path": "/science/crystalline-matrix/overview", "title": "Crystalline Matrix – The Field Behind Matter", "status": "published", "cluster": "crystalline_matrix", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "a62142cb-b6ef-425c-ae66-e3ca8452bb56", "path": "/science/crystalline-matrix/tetrahedral-matrix", "title": "Tetrahedral Matrix – Sulfate, Silica & DNA Hydration", "status": "published", "cluster": "crystalline_matrix", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "df7fd282-9666-4631-98a2-b625f3ea9982", "path": "/science/crystalline-matrix", "title": "Crystalline Matrix: The Geometry of Water, Minerals, and Living Systems", "status": "published", "cluster": "crystalline_matrix", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "0a928cd7-b2e6-4c24-b04a-8ac520a25726", "path": "/science/crystalline-matrix/hexagonal-structures", "title": "Hexagonal Structures – From EZ Water to Mica Layers", "status": "published", "cluster": "crystalline_matrix", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "72afe161-d06e-4c04-a34a-d