e a contemporary, bold sans-serif, optimized for digital legibility (e.g., Google Sans Display). Body text and card content utilize a clean, highly readable sans-serif (e.g., Inter, Open Sans), ensuring accessibility and ease of consumption for scientific information.\n-   **Emotion/Experience**: The page aims to inspire curiosity and a sense of wonder about the fundamental nature of water, positioning it not just as a commodity, but as a dynamic, intelligent medium. The experience is one of guided exploration through complex scientific concepts, made digestible and visually appealing.\n\n**II. LAYOUT STRUCTURE**\n\nThe page follows a clear, responsive, single-column layout, designed to guide the user through the information systematically.\n\n-   **Wireframe & Containers**:\n    -   **Hero Block**: Full viewport width. Contains the main title and lead text, centered horizontally.\n    -   **Main Content Blocks**: Each `andara-section` acts as a distinct, self-contained unit. An `andara-section__inner` container (`max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: ...;`) ensures comfortable reading width and consistent spacing.\n    -   **Grid Elements**: The "Key Properties" and "Further Exploration" sections feature a `andara-grid andara-grid--03` class, arranging cards into a 3-column layout on desktop, intelligently collapsing to 2 or 1 column on smaller devices.\n-   **Rhythm**: Established through consistent vertical padding between sections, alternating background colors for visual separation, and the structured arrangement of content within cards. The linear progression of topics creates a narrative flow.\n\n**III. MOTION LAYOUT STRUCTURE**\n\nMotions on this page are subtle and purposeful, enhancing the theme of discovery and the fluid nature of EZ water, without distracting from the scientific content.\n\n-   **Hero Section**:\n    -   **Headline (`.andara-hero__headline`)**: `entranceMotion`: **Crystalline Bloom** – appears with a gentle scale-in and a soft, expanding glow, as if forming from pure energy. `idleMotion`: **Soft-Pulse** – a very subtle, slow, shimmering glow emanating from the text.\n    -   **Subline (`.andara-hero__subline`)**: `entranceMotion`: **Scalar Slide** – slides in from just below the headline, slightly delayed, with a smooth acceleration. `scrollMotion`: **Magnetic Drift** – as the user scrolls, the hero text elements gently shift towards the center of the viewport, creating a magnetic pull.\n    -   **Hero Background**: `scrollMotion`: **Parallax Depth** – the background image moves slower than the foreground content, creating a subtle sense of depth and immersion into the water theme.\n-   **Section Headers (`.andara-section__header`)**: `entranceMotion`: **Vortex Reveal** – appears with a staggered emergence, almost as if coalescing from the surrounding space, combined with a slight left-to-right `scalarSlide`.\n-   **Paragraph Text**: `entranceMotion`: `fadeIn` with a very slight `riseUp` as it scrolls into view, ensuring smooth content loading.\n-   **Cards (`.andara-card`)**:\n    -   `entranceMotion`: **Krystal Bloom** – each card scales up slightly from its center with a soft glow, revealed in a staggered manner across the grid.\n    -   `idleMotion`: **Micro-Wiggle** – a very subtle, almost imperceptible floating motion, like tiny particles suspended in water.\n    -   `hoverMotion`: **Lift + Shadow Bloom** – cards slightly elevate with a soft, expanding shadow and a gentle blue border glow when hovered over.\n    -   `scrollMotion`: **Staggered Reveal** – cards appear sequentially as they enter the viewport, creating an engaging unfolding effect.\n-   **Andara Buttons (`.andara-button`)**: `hoverMotion`: **Holographic Sheen** – a subtle, iridescent shimmer passes across the button, highlighting its interactive nature.\n\n**IV. MOTION LAYOUT MAP (developer-ready)**\n\n```json\n{\n  "heroHeadline": {\n    "initial": { "opacity": 0, "y": 20, "filter": "blur(5px)" },\n    "animate": { "opacity": 1, "y": 0, "filter": "blur(0px)", "transition": { "duration": 1.2, "ease": "easeOut", "delay": 0.3 } },\n    "idle": "soft-pulse:intensity:0.01:speed:10s",\n    "scroll": "magnetic:center:0.05"\n  },\n  "heroSubline": {\n    "initial": { "opacity": 0, "y": 20, "filter": "blur(5px)" },\n    "animate": { "opacity": 1, "y": 0, "filter": "blur(0px)", "transition": { "duration": 1.2, "ease": "easeOut", "delay": 0.5 } },\n    "idle": "soft-pulse:intensity:0.005:speed:12s",\n    "scroll": "magnetic:center:0.03"\n  },\n  "heroBackground": {\n    "initial": {},\n    "animate": {},\n    "idle": "float:slow:3px",\n    "scroll": "parallax:depth:0.2"\n  },\n  "sectionHeader": {\n    "initial": { "opacity": 0, "x": -20 },\n    "animate": { "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "transition": { "duration": 0.8, "ease": "easeOut" } },\n    "scroll": "staggeredReveal"\n  },\n  "paragraphText": {\n    "initial": { "opacity": 0, "y": 10 },\n    "animate": { "opacity": 1, "y": 0, "transition": { "duration": 0.7, "ease": "easeOut" } },\n    "scroll": "staggeredReveal"\n  },\n  "cards": {\n    "initial": { "opacity": 0, "scale": 0.95, "filter": "blur(3px)" },\n    "animate": { "opacity": 1, "scale": 1, "filter": "blur(0px)", "transition": { "duration": 0.9, "ease": "easeOut", "staggerChildren": 0.1 } },\n    "idle": "micro-wiggle:amplitude:0.5px:speed:3s",\n    "hover": "lift:8px + shadowBloom:15% + borderGlow:blue",\n    "scroll": "staggeredReveal:direction:up"\n  },\n  "andaraButton": {\n    "hover": "holographicSheen"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**V. SIGNATURE ANDARA ATMOSPHERE**\n\nThe "EZ Water – The Fourth Phase" page embodies a **Liquid-Crystal Float** archetype, where the scientific narrative unfolds with a graceful, almost weightless motion. The subtle animations and luminous design elements articulate the bioelectrical nature of structured water, conveying that clarity and energy are inherent in its molecular dance. The experience is both educational and enchanting, inviting users to perceive water not as a static substance, but as a living, energetically charged matrix – a truly holographic and biologically significant phenomenon. The design emphasizes discovery, transforming complex science into an accessible and awe-inspiring journey.	[{"name": "listPages", "result": [{"id": "93310f64-aea0-4d0f-8b79-c836e3c1d025", "path": "/shop/andara-ionic-100ml/faq", "title": "Andara Ionic 100ml – FAQ", "status": "draft", "cluster": "shop", "priority": "P2", "template": "faq"}, {"id": "39c8eb30-60e1-474e-9dec-8b940f27eb2b", "path": "/shop/andara-ionic-1l/faq", "title": "Andara Ionic 1L – FAQ", "status": "draft", "cluster": "shop", "priority": "P2", "template": "faq"}, {"id": "dc4dd9b2-6350-4eee-8edd-95f141ef6244", "path": "/how-to-use-andara/household", "title": "Household Water Usage", "status": "draft", "cluster": "shop", "priority": "P2", "template": "guide"}, {"id": "f3d0d43f-c826-479d-bf10-8f56f943f1c7", "path": "/trust/lab-reports", "title": "Lab Reports & Certifications", "status": "draft", "cluster": "trust", "priority": "P2", "template": "lab_data"}, {"id": "602a184d-93be-496e-ba1c-89c3b61b268a", "path": "/science/microbiome-minerals/mineral-roots", "title": "Mineral Roots of the Microbiome", "status": "draft", "cluster": "microbiome", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "1de4a9bc-2443-4dfc-bbf7-61ae7cd90a00", "path": "/science/mineral-sources/ocean-water", "title": "Ocean Water Minerals", "status": "draft", "cluster": "mineral_sources", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "4e6df026-0380-4b07-bceb-6e452e3a1909", "path": "/about/our-story", "title": "Our Story – From Volcanic Origins to Your Glass", "status": "draft", "cluster": "about", "priority": "P2", "template": "about"}, {"id": "c6c72739-5394-4976-abb5-7a96b30f06ff", "path": "/science/dna/what-is-dna", "title": "What is DNA? – The Code of Life", "status": "draft", "cluster": "dna", "priority": "P2", "template": "article"}, {"id": "9ea7915f-08cc-4877-a939-77cd4aab0747", "path": "/shop