ional determinations in the system H 2 O-Na-Ca-Cl-SO 4 - ResearchGate, https://www.researchgate.net/publication/316450255_Sulfate_brines_in_fluid_inclusions_of_hydrothermal_veins_Compositional_determinations_in_the_system_H_2_O-Na-Ca-Cl-SO_4\n34. Major Styles of Mineralization and Hydrothermal Alteration and Related Solid- and Aqueous-Phase Geochemical Signatures - USGS Publications Warehouse, https://pubs.usgs.gov/pp/1651/downloads/Vol1_combinedChapters/vol1_chapE3.pdf\n35. Gypsum - Wikipedia, https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gypsum\n36. The Many Benefits of Gypsum, Anhydrite, and Limestone - Arcosa Specialty Materials, https://arcosaspecialtymaterials.com/the-many-benefits-of-gypsum-anhydrite-and-limestone/\n37. Industrial Applications | K+S Aktiengesellschaft, https://www.kpluss.com/en-us/our-business-products/industry/industrial-applications/\n38. Sulfate & Health - California Air Resources Board - CA.gov, https://ww2.arb.ca.gov/resources/sulfate-and-health\n39. Sulfates & Sulfides in Well Water - IN.gov, https://www.in.gov/health/eph/well-water-quality-and-testing/sulfates-and-sulfides-in-well-water/\n40. Sulfate - NM-Tracking, https://nmtracking.doh.nm.gov/environment/water/Sulfate.html\n41. Acid Mine Drainage Remediation: Sulfate Removal Methods - Farmonaut, https://farmonaut.com/mining/acid-mine-drainage-remediation-sulfate-removal-methods\n42. In-situ Remediation of Sulfate Contamination Using ... - Acta Scientific, https://actascientific.com/ASMI/pdf/ASMI-05-1085.pdf\n43. Sulfate-Reducing Bacteria as an Effective Tool for Sustainable Acid Mine Bioremediation, https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC6113391/\n44. (PDF) Unlocking soil revival: the role of sulfate-reducing bacteria in mitigating heavy metal contamination - ResearchGate, https://www.researchgate.net/publication/383824531_Unlocking_soil_revival_the_role_of_sulfate-reducing_bacteria_in_mitigating_heavy_metal_contamination	\N	\N	2025-12-11 09:28:06.457392
