t-lead`\n    (larger size or stronger weight).\n  - Use generous spacing between `.andara-hero__bullets` for scannability.\n  - Ensure the phrase “Andara Ionic 100 ml” appears clearly above the fold.\n\n  Imagery:\n  - Render a photorealistic dark glass 100 ml bottle with Andara branding.\n  - Hero concept: left side a slightly cloudy glass (before), right side a clear,\n    luminous glass (after Andara). Between them, faint hexagonal crystalline pattern.\n  - Background: deep indigo–blue gradient, subtle bokeh, hint of lab + nature.\n\n  CTA:\n  - Style `.andara-hero__cta--primary` as a single dominant button.\n  - `.andara-hero__support-link` is a smaller, underlined text link beneath.\n  -->\n\n  <!-- ===========================\n       SECTION 2 – WHAT IT IS\n  ============================ -->\n  <section\n    id="product-100ml-what-it-is"\n    class="andara-section andara-section--what-it-is"\n    aria-label="What Andara Ionic 100 ml is"\n  >\n    <div class="andara-section__inner">\n      <header class="andara-section__header">\n        <h2 class="andara-section__headline">\n          What is Andara Ionic 100&nbsp;ml?\n        </h2>\n        <p class="andara-section__subline">\n          A <strong>100&nbsp;ml bottle of ionic sulfate mineral drops</strong> for water\n          treatment and clarification – not a supplement, not a medicine.\n        </p>\n      </header>\n\n      <div class="andara-grid andara-grid--02">\n        <article class="andara-grid__item">\n          <h3 class="andara-grid__title">Ionic sulfate mineral concentrate</h3>\n          <p class="andara-grid__text">\n            Andara Ionic is a <strong>liquid mineral complex</strong> made from\n            deeply sourced volcanic minerals. The minerals are present in\n            <strong>ionic, sulfate-bound form</strong>, meaning they are fully\n            dissolved, electrically charged and able to interact directly\n            with water chemistry.\n          </p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class="andara-grid__item">\n          <h3 class="andara-grid__title">Designed for water – not the body</h3>\n          <p class="andara-grid__text">\n            The <strong>intended use</strong> of Andara Ionic 100&nbsp;ml is to treat\n            water: support clarification, flocculation, mineral balance and\n            structured-water formation. It is <strong>not positioned as a dietary\n            supplement</strong> and does not make health or disease claims.\n          </p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class="andara-grid__item">\n          <h3 class="andara-grid__title">100&nbsp;ml: the personal exploration format</h3>\n          <p class="andara-grid__text">\n            The 100&nbsp;ml bottle is ideal for <strong>personal use, travel,\n            small households and first-time testers</strong>. It gives you enough\n            mineral concentrate to work with multiple liters of water, track\n            visible changes, and decide if you want to move into liter-size\n            bottles or bundles later.\n          </p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class="andara-grid__item">\n          <h3 class="andara-grid__title">Part of a larger science ecosystem</h3>\n          <p class="andara-grid__text">\n            Andara Ionic 100&nbsp;ml connects into the full <strong>Andara Science\n            Library</strong>: water science, mineral chemistry, crystalline matrix,\n            and bioelectric concepts. Every product page links directly into\n            background articles, lab protocols and structured-water guides.\n          </p>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- AI LAYOUT PROMPT – WHAT IT IS\n  Layout:\n  - Use `.andara-section--what-it-is` with an inner container `.andara-section__inner`.\n  - Add `.andara-grid.andara-grid--02` to create a responsive 2x2 card layout:\n    - On desktop: 2 columns, 2 rows.\n    - On mobile: stack `.andara-grid__item` vertically.\n\n  Typography: