ured water and mineral matrices."}, {"section": "WHAT IS BIOELECTRICITY?", "layoutSpec": "Header with headline and subline, followed by a 2-column grid and a full-width figure.", "layoutClass": ".andara-section, .andara-grid--02", "motionItems": [{"preset": "scroll-fade-up", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-what-is-it", "targetDescription": "The entire section container"}, {"preset": "scroll-fade-up-stagger", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-what-is-it .andara-grid__item", "targetDescription": "Cards within the 2-column grid"}], "colorPalette": ["deep indigo", "electric turquoise", "soft gold"], "vibeKeywords": ["bioelectric grid", "scientific", "educational"], "emotionalTone": ["clarity", "revelation"], "responsiveSpec": "Grid stacks to a single column on mobile.", "imageryDescription": "Infographic showing scaling of bioelectricity from cell to tissue to whole-body field."}, {"section": "CELL VOLTAGE & PROTON GRADIENTS", "layoutSpec": "Header followed by a 3-column grid of articles, and a final full-width graph figure.", "layoutClass": ".andara-section, .andara-grid--03", "motionItems": [{"preset": "scroll-fade-up", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-cell-voltage", "targetDescription": "The entire section container"}, {"preset": "scroll-fade-up-stagger", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-cell-voltage .andara-grid__item", "targetDescription": "Cards within the 3-column grid"}], "colorPalette": ["deep indigo", "electric turquoise", "soft gold"], "vibeKeywords": ["cellular", "scientific", "diagrammatic"], "emotionalTone": ["precision", "clarity"], "responsiveSpec": "Grid stacks to a single column on mobile.", "imageryDescription": "A graph showing 'Membrane Potential' vs 'Cell State' with zones for 'Undercharged', 'Balanced', 'Over-excited'."}, {"section": "WATER, MINERALS & THE WIRING OF LIFE", "layoutSpec": "Header followed by a 2-column grid of articles, and a final full-width infographic.", "layoutClass": ".andara-section, .andara-grid--02", "motionItems": [{"preset": "scroll-fade-up", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-water-minerals", "targetDescription": "The entire section container"}, {"preset": "scroll-fade-up-stagger", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-water-minerals .andara-grid__item", "targetDescription": "Cards within the 2-column grid"}], "colorPalette": ["deep indigo", "electric turquoise", "soft gold"], "vibeKeywords": ["liquid crystal", "conductive", "elemental"], "emotionalTone": ["wonder", "connection"], "responsiveSpec": "Grid stacks to a single column on mobile.", "imageryDescription": "Layered infographic showing hexagonal water layers around a protein, with ionic sulfate minerals interspersed as nodes, and arrows indicating charge flow."}, {"section": "FROM NOISE TO COHERENCE TIMELINE", "layoutSpec": "Header followed by a 4-step horizontal timeline, and a final full-width visual summarizing the timeline.", "layoutClass": ".andara-section, .andara-grid--timeline", "motionItems": [{"preset": "scroll-fade-up", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": "#bioelectricity-coherence-timeline", "targetDescription": "The entire section container"}, {"preset": "scroll-fade-up-stagger", "trigger": "scroll", "targetSelector": ".andara-grid--timeline .andara-grid__item", "targetDescription": "Steps within the timeline grid"}], "colorPalette": ["deep indigo", "electric turquoise", "soft gold"], "vibeKeywords": ["narrative", "progression", "hopeful"], "emotionalTone": ["clarity", "empowerment"], "responsiveSpec": "Timeline steps stack vertically on mobile.", "imageryDescription": "A 4-panel visual storyboard showing the transition from chaotic waveforms to smooth field lines around a human silhouette, connected by a glowing line."}], "imagePrompts": [{"id": "img-hero", "prompt": "A stylized human silhouette made of soft light lines, surrounded by gently glowing field lines and ion streams, standing in a dark indigo space. Fine turquoise currents flow along meridian-like paths, with golden nodes marking voltage hubs. In the background: hexagonal and wave-like geometry, hinting at liquid crystal water and minerals. Mood: calm, powerful, scientific yet mystical.", "location": "Top-level ANDARA VISUAL CONFIG comment", "generated": false}, {"id": "img-diagram-what-is-it", "prompt": "Infographic: a simple diagram showing: (1) individual cell with membrane potential, (2) cluster of cells forming a tissue with a voltage gradient arrow, (3) a larger outline of a body with field lines around it. Each level labelled “Cell Voltage”, “Tissue Gradient”, “Whole-Body Field”.", "location": "Comment in #bioelectricity-what-is-it section", "generated": false}, {"id": "img-graph-cell-voltage", "prompt": "Graph: gentle curve showing “Membrane Potential” on the vertical axis vs “Cell State” on the horizontal axis. Different zones labelled “Undercharged”, “Balanced”, “Over-excited” to visualise that both extremes can disturb terrain coherence.", "location": "Comment in #bioelectricity-cell-voltage section", "generated": false}, {"id": "img-infographic-wiring", "prompt": "Infographic: layered illustration: (1) hexagonal water layers around a protein, (2) ions (sulfate, magnesium, etc.) interspersed as nodes, (3) arrows showing current flowing along this hydrated matrix. Caption labels: “Structured Water”, “Ionic Sulfate Minerals”, “Charge Flow”.", "location": "Comment in #bioelectricity-water-minerals section", "generated": false}, {"id": "img-timeline-coherence", "prompt": "Timeline visual: 4 panels from left to right: (1) chaotic waveforms and noisy fields, (2) water droplet + filter icon, (3) hexagonal water + ionic nodes, (4) smooth field lines around a human silhouette. A gentle glowing line connects them all.", "location": "Comment in #bioelectricity-coherence-timeline section", "generated": false}], "suggestedSeo": {"title": "Bioelectricity: The Invisible Voltage System of Life | Andara", "description": "Discover bioelectricity, the invisible voltage architecture that shapes regeneration and terrain. Learn how ion currents, water, and minerals form a living circuit.", "focusKeyword": "Bioelectric Terrain"}, "videoPrompts": [{"id": "vid-hero-bg", "prompt": "Looped animation of a human outline, viewed from front, with slow-moving electric currents flowing along meridian-like lines and around the body as a softly pulsing field. The surrounding space shows faint, moving hexagonal patterns and waves, representing structured water and bioelectric flow. Motion is slow and meditative, not aggressive.", "location": "Top-level ANDARA VISUAL CONFIG comment"}], "visualConfig": {"priority": "P1", "vibeKeywords": ["bioelectric grid", "auric field", "ion currents", "liquid crystal body", "cosmic nervous system", "deep indigo", "electric turquoise", "soft gold accents"], "aiImagePrompt": "A stylized human silhouette made of soft light lines, surrounded by gently glowing field lines and ion streams, standing in a dark indigo space. Fine turquoise currents flow along meridian-like paths, with golden nodes marking voltage hubs. In the background: hexagonal and wave-like geometry, hinting at liquid crystal water and minerals. Mood: calm, powerful, scientific yet mystical.", "aiVideoPrompt": "Looped animation of a human outline, viewed from front, with slow-moving electric currents flowing along meridian-like lines and around the body as a softly pulsing field. The surrounding space shows faint, moving hexagonal patterns and waves, representing structured water and bioelectric flow. Motion is slow and meditative, not aggressive.", "designerNotes": "This page should feel like opening the 'wiring diagram' behind life. Show voltage, ion flow, and fields in a non-medical, terrain-focused way. Combine scientific diagrams (graphs, gradients, vector flows) with subtle spiritual-electric aesthetics. Use motion to make invisible fields intuitive, not overwhelming.", "emotionalTone": ["revelation", "awe", "inner-recognition", "calm power", "precision", "future-organic"], "animationIdeas": ["slowly pulsing field lines around a human silhouette", "glowing pathways along fascia-like lines when scrolling", "subtle particle flows moving along gradient lines", "hover: cards reveal tiny sparks along edges", "timeline: voltage pulses moving from left to right", "background: faint moving field geometry"]}, "animationSpecs": [{"spec": "On scroll into view, the entire section fades in and slides up by 24px (scroll-fade-up).", "element": "motion.section"}, {"spec": "On scroll into view, grid items fade in and slide up sequentially with a 0.06s stagger delay (scroll-fade-up-stagger).", "element": ".andara-grid__item"}, {"spec": "On mount, the element infinitely loops a scaling animation from 1 to 1.03 and back, creating a gentle breathing effect (ambient-breathing).", "element": ".andara-hero__media-placeholder"}], "suggestedLinks": [{"anchor": "100 ml", "reason": "Direct link to a specific product page from the product cross-link section.", "targetPath": "/shop/andara-ionic-100ml"}, {"anchor": "1 L", "reason": "Direct link to a specific product page from the product cross-link section.", "targetPath": "/shop/andara-ionic-1l"}, {"anchor": "Go to Water Science →", "reason": "Navigates to the Water Science pillar in the science library footer.", "targetPath": "/science/water"}, {"anchor": "Go to Mineral Science →", "reason": "Navigates to the Mineral Science pillar in the science library footer.", "targetPath": "/science/minerals"}, {"anchor": "Go to Crystalline Matrix →", "reason": "Navigates to the Crystalline Matrix pillar in the science library footer.", "targetPath": "/science/crystalline-matrix"}, {"anchor": "Go to Terrain & Regeneration →", "reason": "Navigates to the Terrain & Regeneration pillar in the science library footer.", "targetPath": "/science/terrain-regeneration"}, {"anchor": "Explore Andara Ionic Formats", "reason": 